  "description": "<h4>Application:</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Mazda RX-7 FC3S 1987-1991</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Package Includes:</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Front coilovers × 2</li>\n<li>Rear coilovers × 2</li>\n<li>Spanner × 2</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Features:</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Mono-tube shock design, provides larger oil &amp; gas capacity</li>\n<li>Adjustable ride height</li>\n<li>Adjustable pre-load spring tension</li>\n<li>Pillow-ball top mount reduces noise, sharpens steering feel &amp; response</li>\n<li>High-tensile performance spring: &lt; 0.04 % distortion after 600 k cycles, surface-treated for durability</li>\n<li>Rubber boots included on all inserts to protect dampers &amp; keep them clean</li>\n<li>Better handling without sacrificing ride comfort</li>\n<li>Quick, cost-effective way to upgrade your car's appearance</li>\n<li>Easy installation with proper tools</li>\n<li>Suitable for track, drift, fast-road, and daily driving</li>\n<li>All pictured accessories included</li>\n<li>Default 1-year warranty for any manufacturing defect, upgrade to 2 years with our Extended Warranty Program</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Warranty</h4>\n<p>All products carry a standard 1-year warranty from the date of purchase. A proof of purchase (order number preferred) is required. To expedite any warranty claim, please provide clear photos/videos and detailed descriptions; in most cases the defective item does not need to be returned. Additional information may be requested to accurately diagnose and resolve the issue.</p>",
